---
description: File and object storage rules
globs:
  - "apps/backend/**/files/**/*.kt"
  - "apps/backend/**/documents/**/*.kt"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Storage Rules

- Only the files module may call object storage directly.
- Never expose public object storage URLs.
- Store FileObject metadata and hashes.
- Downloads require backend authorization.
- Uploads require validation and audit events.
